N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 5 ยง 103.11 - Briefs

State Regulations

Briefs, in triplicate, may be filed by any party to the
proceedings, and will become a part of the record, provided copies thereof are
first served upon all parties, and the original with affidavit of service is
submitted within the time fixed by the hearing officer. Notes
